## Architecture Summary

Data (campaign dict) -> Input normalization -> Phase 2 preprocessor (parse/date/ratio/OHE/scaling) -> Stage 1 quantile LightGBM models (5 metrics x q10/q50/q90) -> Stage 2 XGBoost ROI regressor + XGBoost success classifier -> ROI + success probability + verdict (+ SHAP explanation)

